reviews.review_text: Done It Again While there is another Matrix of this show available, this one has a much fuller sound with Phil's work thundering along with just the right amount of thump. Fantastic show with a fantastic Matrix. Thanks for all the hard work.

Hot damn Grateful for this. Just listened to Dave's 53, loved it, and this is the night before. Hunter Seamon's matrix is my personal gold standard for production quality, and this fits the bill. Great show to boot.
